isited</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Chemical Engineering Science</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/99fc5b106954e9e32c385e6cfb310271"><gtr:id>99fc5b106954e9e32c385e6cfb310271</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Hounslow M</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2013-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>5675f0535c28a</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>3BC36A91-9FFA-4ACD-A731-DE2E4B093BD2</gtr:id><gtr:title>Micro-mechanical model of calcium oxalate monohydrate aggregation in supersaturated solutions: Effect of crystal form and seed concentration</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Journal of Crystal Growth</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/af44156afdbcc0c5ad1dfdb3058067e5"><gtr:id>af44156afdbcc0c5ad1dfdb3058067e5</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Pitt K</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2012-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>doi_53cff9ff95a0f2d5</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>BE91FCD3-5F27-42D7-B442-C1B8601CC93A</gtr:id><gtr:title>Aggregation of growing crystals in suspension: III. Accounting for adhesion and repulsion</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Chemical Engineering Science</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/af44156afdbcc0c5ad1dfdb3058067e5"><gtr:id>af44156afdbcc0c5ad1dfdb3058067e5</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Pitt K</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2015-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>5675f0540dd59</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>CCEF7101-2BBC-4EA9-A479-BBC8C133DE9E</gtr:id><gtr:title>Aggregation of growing crystals in suspension: II. Poiseuille flow crystalliser</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Chemical Engineering Science</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/af44156afdbcc0c5ad1dfdb3058067e5"><gtr:id>af44156afdbcc0c5ad1dfdb3058067e5</gtr:i